{
  "stem": "8352.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They pushed us and those trains in about 80 to 100 people in one of those wagons.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It only had a little window there for a little air.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were traveling for about three to four days until we came into that Mateszalka, to that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That was somewhere in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there were coming in troops and groups of people every day, because they were going from village to village to village and collecting and gathering all the Jewish people and taking them out of there.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was no one village left that they shouldn't have gone and searched and-- and get all the Jews out of there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "On the way to that ghetto, it was horrible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was-- it was hot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was no air.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Children were crying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "People were getting sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We had no air, no bathroom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They opened the door maybe once or twice a day just for a few minutes to let a little air in there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was terrible-- screaming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] People were getting very sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were-- they were-- they were getting-- passing out because of the heat in there and-- and no room to move.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We were just put in like sardines.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Our parents told us nobody is going-- some of the guys wanted to run away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They thought maybe run away, maybe we will-- we will survive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The parents didn't want to let the children go nowhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They said, we are going to be together until the end.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Whatever will happen to one will happen to all of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we had to respect our parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We did very much respect our parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
